Cleverbot.py - an API for Cleverbot in Python
=============================================

Comments/pull requests/feedback welcome!

Usage
-----

Taken from cleverbot/cleverbot.py:150-161

```
>>> if __name__ == "__main__":
    cb1 = Cleverbot()
    cb2 = Cleverbot()

    resp1 = cb1.ask("Hello.")
    print "Bob:", "Hello"

    while True:
        print "Alice:", resp1
        resp2 = cb2.ask(resp1)
        print "Bob:", resp2
        resp1 = cb1.ask(resp2)
```
